    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a new legal designation for political parties as distinct legal entities",
        "additional_details": "We think creating a new legal designation for political parties would promote transparency in politics. Additionally, we think it could foster a change in mindset: from political organisations fixated on their own goals to those dedicated to public service, as originally intended. Ultimately, we think this change could help build public trust in politics.",
        "background": "Create a new legal designation for political parties to prevent them from acting as corporations.",
